I want to share my insight (on my quite time). I belive that bible is the way of communicating and connect with God. It is letting Him speak to us and bring us closer to Him. If we treat God as a Living God, His presence will be strong in our life. And we can be more like Him by understanding God's character through Bible, it reflects on our life. Have we still sin against one another?  Still do what is wrong eventhough we know it is wrong and make God unhappy? Some people have wrong intention-- they says bible is to heal you. To worhsip God will give you blessing. It is wrong to focus on the benefit for ourselves. God will give blessing and healing according to His will and plan.
Focusing on our relationship with God by reading the Bible everyday. Treat God as our King, our Father, our Bestfriend and put Him on priority. Treat Him as a LIVING GOD. Then everything will be given to you automatically.
